Quote:  The Harrow that is proving ideal for use on 95 per cent. of our pastures is the Fertility Harrow. The light-weight job has short knife-edged spring steel teeth which give a clean surface .. For this work, the fertility harrow has probably the most efficient manure spreading device ever built .. The Fertility harrows are sufficiently light in draught ...
